    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "proxy_list",
      "x": 110, "y": 315,
      "width": 320, "height": 160,
      "text": "Axum proxies to all services:\n├── /api/messages/* → BlueBubbles (iMessage)\n├── /api/chat/*     → OpenClaw (AI agents)\n├── /api/vault/*    → CouchDB (Obsidian notes)\n├── /api/reminders  → Mac Bridge (Apple)\n├── /api/homelab    → Proxmox / OPNsense\n├── /api/calendar   → CalDAV (iCloud)\n├── /api/auth/*     → Supabase Auth\n├── /api/todos      → Supabase (via sync)\n└── /api/events     → Supabase Realtime",
      "originalText": "Axum proxies to all services:\n├── /api/messages/* → BlueBubbles (iMessage)\n├── /api/chat/*     → OpenClaw (AI agents)\n├── /api/vault/*    → CouchDB (Obsidian notes)\n├── /api/reminders  → Mac Bridge (Apple)\n├── /api/homelab    → Proxmox / OPNsense\n├── /api/calendar   → CalDAV (iCloud)\n├── /api/auth/*     → Supabase Auth\n├── /api/todos      → Supabase (via sync)\n└── /api/events     → Supabase Realtime",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
