    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "services_extras",
      "x": 590, "y": 335,
      "width": 330, "height": 160,
      "text": "Also running on Services VM:\n├── CouchDB (Obsidian LiveSync)\n├── Vaultwarden (password manager)\n├── Firecrawl (web scraping)\n└── Docker + Portainer\n\nAll services bound to 127.0.0.1\nExposed only via Tailscale IPs\nUFW firewall + fail2ban active",
      "originalText": "Also running on Services VM:\n├── CouchDB (Obsidian LiveSync)\n├── Vaultwarden (password manager)\n├── Firecrawl (web scraping)\n└── Docker + Portainer\n\nAll services bound to 127.0.0.1\nExposed only via Tailscale IPs\nUFW firewall + fail2ban active",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
