    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "auth_details",
      "x": 80, "y": 820,
      "width": 840, "height": 80,
      "text": "Layer 1: MC_API_KEY (rotates every launch) + MC_AGENT_KEY (stable, for Bjorn) — constant-time comparison\nLayer 2: Tailscale ACLs — WireGuard mutual auth, only tailnet members can connect\nLayer 3: Cloudflare Access — GitHub/Google OAuth on *.aparcedo.org subdomains\n\nAll data endpoints require MFA-verified session · 24h hard session expiry · AES-256-GCM encrypted secrets",
      "originalText": "Layer 1: MC_API_KEY (rotates every launch) + MC_AGENT_KEY (stable, for Bjorn) — constant-time comparison\nLayer 2: Tailscale ACLs — WireGuard mutual auth, only tailnet members can connect\nLayer 3: Cloudflare Access — GitHub/Google OAuth on *.aparcedo.org subdomains\n\nAll data endpoints require MFA-verified session · 24h hard session expiry · AES-256-GCM encrypted secrets",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#94a3b8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
